	<dl>
	<dt>I can't support my first choice: Conservatives...</dt>
	<dd><p>I can't support my first choice: Conservatives - they have simply become too racist in their campaigning against immigration (and 'my grandmother died in the Holocaust' from Mr Howard does not prove the contrary.  I won't support Labour because of Tony Blair. I won't support LibDems because of the unpleasant experience in my constituency: Dr Jenny Tonge MP, now retiring, but 'friend' of current candidate.<br />UKIP and Greens are obviously going nowhere.</p>
	<small>
	written 18th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1016">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1016">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

