	<p><em><strong>SDC</strong> replies:</em> Out of interest, is 'our' country actually becoming more overcrowded? Is the population any larger than, say, 10 , 20 or 50 years ago?<br />The only justification for restricting immigration ought to be public health or national security. Apart from that, if people want to come here for a better life, then let them. The US has prospered on such an approach.</p>
